room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Excape Games in Clarksville
room_description: Part of your group has been wrongfully arrested for a bank robbery and are being held at a local jail. The others are new deputies that have begun to suspect there is something strange going on in the Sherriffâ€™s department. While the Sheriff is out, your group has one hour to prove the innocence of the incarcerated team members and find your way out of the jail. You will need to work together as if all your lives depended on it because they just might!
